<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 01:01:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着交易员评估伊朗的波动性，比特币小幅下跌</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-btc-edges-downward-as-traders-take-stock-of-iran-volatility</link><description>随着投资者消化美国经济数据的发布并应对中东的事态发展，比特币跌破 68,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igIKnsTrADrc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 11:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-btc-edges-downward-as-traders-take-stock-of-iran-volatility</guid></item><item><title>随着波动性的回归，比特币与股票的相关性飙升</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-s-correlation-with-stocks-surges-as-volatility-returns</link><description>比特币再次与美国股市密切同步，这对加密货币顽固分子来说几乎是最糟糕的时刻。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOpaLmZrsPf8/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 20:35:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-s-correlation-with-stocks-surges-as-volatility-returns</guid></item><item><title>美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 结束针对加密货币亿万富翁贾斯汀·孙 (Justin Sun) 的诉讼</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/sec-ends-case-against-crypto-billionaire-justin-sun</link><description>美国证券交易委员会表示，随着监管机构继续解决拜登政府期间提起的大量数字资产执法案件，它将结束对加密货币亿万富翁孙宇晨及其附属公司的诉讼，并将支付 1000 万美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iq5PO.foQG2M/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 21:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/sec-ends-case-against-crypto-billionaire-justin-sun</guid></item><item><title>纽约证券交易所所有者以 250 亿美元估值投资加密货币公司</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/nyse-owner-invests-in-crypto-exchange-at-25-billion-valuation</link><description>InterContinental Exchange Inc. 在一笔交易中收购了 OKX 的股份，该交易对这家加密货币交易运营商的估值为 250 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iX9U6LVeDTsY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 12:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/nyse-owner-invests-in-crypto-exchange-at-25-billion-valuation</guid></item><item><title>SEC 杠杆 ETF 在即将到来的加密货币洪水面前冻结</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-05/the-sec-s-leveraged-etf-freeze-ahead-of-the-looming-crypto-flood</link><description>在特朗普政府采取更加宽松的监管态度的背景下，美国证券交易委员会对日益激进的基金结构提出了担忧。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.6x4qVOHFlE/v8/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-05/the-sec-s-leveraged-etf-freeze-ahead-of-the-looming-crypto-flood</guid></item><item><title>由于伊朗动荡笼罩市场，比特币的涨势动摇</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/bitcoin-btc-holds-firm-above-70-000-as-global-assets-recover</link><description>比特币正在努力维持上涨势头，而全球市场在伊朗持续冲突造成数日波动后仍面临压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ig2GanXlEmLA/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 02:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/bitcoin-btc-holds-firm-above-70-000-as-global-assets-recover</guid></item></channel></rss>